questiondata.strat-other: Each new list started a new visualization, where I saw each of the words being represented in a scenario. Fr example, I imagined an ACTOR (Johnny Depp) wearing an APRON, and announcing he will be my SERVER outside of a WARDROBE I was picking a BLOUSE out of while on a CLOUD because I just died due to a VIRUS, and oh look, there is a DRAGON that looks like a PUPPY (Falcor). It was fun. And challenging. lol
